node.text:
I really debated all day wether i was going to post the whole video or not... it was so many things that i would have done differently like redo the whole video because of the mess ups, tightened up my arms a little bit , make facials or be more loose and free with my moves...but i had to remember that this was my first dance class that is also out of my comfort zone...I have a whole lot of improving to do but i know ill get better. @officialbelieve3 thank you so much for this experience i really enjoyed it & i’ll be looking forward to the next one!! ❤️❤️
Dancers: @semaj_lesley and @lavish.camm 
Choreo: @officialbelieve3
